# Grouped Flowchart Test
@diagram|id:grouped-test|type:flow|purpose:Test with subgraphs|direction:TD

@group|id:input|label:Input Stage
@group|id:process|label:Processing

@node|id:A|label:Start|group:input
@node|id:B|label:Validate|group:input
@node|id:C|label:Transform|group:process
@node|id:D|label:Output|group:process

@edge|from:A|to:B
@edge|from:B|to:C
@edge|from:C|to:D
